{"tid":1676778,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃之鋒重申　不支持香港獨立作為民主自決的一個選項","createTime":"2019-10-26T16:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T16:40:18.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e663598969e6d2f772e4d69229e239ba4d744b73","tid":1676778,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:16:31.000Z","msg":"區議會南區海怡西選區參選人黃之鋒收到新任南區選舉主任蔡亮的來信，第三度查問其政治主張。黃之鋒在社交網站公開他的回覆，表示選舉主任錯誤地理解他對民主自決的主張，重申不支持香港獨立作為民主自決的一個選項。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒強調香港眾志與他支持的前途自決，應該在一國兩制的憲政框架內進行，任何成為自決前途選項的主張，先決條件是擁有相當民意基礎。<br />\n<br />\n對於蔡亮引用一篇他在去年回應譚耀宗的新聞，要求黃之鋒就該篇報道作回應，黃之鋒在回信中表示，認為該報道與選舉主任考慮提名並無關連。<br />\n<br />\n海怡西選區其他參選人包括新民黨陳家珮及報稱民主派的林浩波。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488369-20191026.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488369-20191026.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjgDpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=c4277afc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488369-20191026.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3814b5d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488369-20191026.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"1a2031ebdc278ce0d53a1f93c409864f53e29b7f","tid":1676778,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:17:13.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbaf4dcebe0f9e953d20bde26dd8620f5e80a4e8","tid":1676778,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG9c5Um.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG9c5Um.gif&h=4ad4d108&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b3041b88063f545b39e866d9f6b31264ac7abde","tid":16